<plot>SPARKLE is a contemporary comedy about life, love and relationships in the twenty first century, from the directors of Lawless Heart. Sam is a charming, young schemer who has ambitions in the glamorous world of public relations when he moves to London. However, his best laid plans suffer a real setback when true love turns his world upside down in the most unexpected of circumstances.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?509331</url></doc>
